{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 42,
  "title": "第四十二章（道化）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "道生一，"
    },
    {
      "text": "一生二，"
    },
    {
      "text": "二生三，"
    },
    {
      "text": "三生萬物。"
    },
    {
      "text": "萬物負陰而抱陽，"
    },
    {
      "text": "沖氣以為和。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之所惡，惟孤﹑寡﹑不轂，而王公以為稱。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故物或損之而益，"
    },
    {
      "text": "或益之而損。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之所教，"
    },
    {
      "text": "我亦教之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "強梁者不得其死，"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾將以為教父。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道使所生者一也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "一生陰與陽也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "陰陽生和、清、濁三氣，分為天地人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地人共生萬物也，天施地化，人長養之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "萬物無不負陰而向陽，迴心而就日。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "萬物中皆有元氣，得以和柔，若胸中有藏，骨中有髓，草木中有空虛與氣通，故得久生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孤寡不轂者，不祥之名，而王公以為稱者，處謙卑，法空虛和柔。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "引之不得，推之必還。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫增高者志崩，貪富者致患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂眾人所教，去弱為強，去柔為剛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言我教眾人，使去強為弱，去柔為剛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "強粱者，謂不信玄妙，背叛道德，不從經教，尚勢任力也。不得其死者，為天命所絕，兵刃所伐，王法所殺，不得以壽命死。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "父，使也。老子以強梁之人為教，誡之始也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
